This document is the API specification for citygml4j 1.0.
citygml4j is a Java class library for facilitating work with the City Geography Markup Language (CityGML).
citygml4j is open source and released under the terms of the GNU Lesser General Public License v3 (LGPL).
Official website and more information at: http://www.igg.tu-berlin.de/software/
